.name
ADtoHT
.fullname
autodocs to hypertext
.type
OS Utility
.short
Convert autodocs to AmigaGuide format
.description
Converts autodoc files to AmigaGuide format, creating links
to referenced functions (both within the same autodoc
file and to other files) and structures (i.e. links into
the include-files). As a result, it is very easy to read
the converted autodocs.
.version
1.01
.date
1993.03.30
.author
Christian Stieber
.restrictions
XREF file not usable. Some options don't work.
Use the current version from aminet, if possible. However,
this version should do fine if you don't try anything "fancy".
.requirements
Requires AmigaOS V37 (2.04)
