.comment
I recommend that you do not use this version of ADtoHT, although it probably
does work well for you. Use the current version available on aminet (today,
Feb 19, 1994: version 1.3). Currently I intend to completely rewrite this
program since the source is pretty messed up, and some things are not really
useful the way they are implemented now (reading xref files). However, I have
not yet started to work on version 2.0, and I don't know when I will start
working on it.
